"_blank\">Rising Restrictions on Religion<\/a>, <\/em>which talks about religious tolerance (and intolerance) in the countries around the world. Are nations becoming more restrictive about religion? Are they becoming more accepting?<\/p>\n<p>But perhaps the toughest controversy of all is addressed: was KITT from <em>Knight Rider <\/em>voiced by the guy who played Mr. Belvedere?<\/p>\n<p>Join us for this special episode &#8212; and share your thoughts with us! Do so here, on <a title=\"Facebook: Hey! That's My Hummus!\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/HeyThatsMyHummus\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook <\/a>or on <a title=\"Twitter - Hey! That's My Hummus!\" href=\"http:\/\/twitter.com\/#!\/thatsmyhummus\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<div class=\"powerpress_player\" id=\"powerpress_player_8245\"><!--[if lt IE 9]><script>document.createElement('audio');<\/script><![endif]-->\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-408-1\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio\/mpeg\" src=\"http:\/\/media.blubrry.com\/heythatsmyhummus\/www.heythatsmyhummus.com\/podcasts\/HeyThatsMyHummus-022.mp3?_=1\" \/><a href=\"http:\/\/media.blubrry.com\/heythatsmyhummus\/www.heythatsmyhummus.com\/podcasts\/HeyThatsMyHummus-022.mp3\">http:\/\/media.blubrry.com\/heythatsmyhummus\/www.heythatsmyhummus.com\/podcasts\/HeyThatsMyHummus-022.mp3<\/a><\/audio><\/div><p class=\"powerpress_links powerpress_links_mp3\">Podcast: <a href=\"http:\/\/media.blubrry.com\/heythatsmyhummus\/www.heythatsmyhummus.com\/podcasts\/HeyThatsMyHummus-022.mp3\" class=\"powerpress_link_pinw\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Play in new window\" onclick=\"return powerpress_pinw('https:\/\/www.HeyThatsMyHummus.com\/?powerpress_pinw=408-podcast');\" rel=\"nofollow\">Play in new window<\/a> | <a href=\"http:\/\/media.blubrry.com\/heythatsmyhummus\/www.heythatsmyhummus.com\/podcasts\/HeyThatsMyHummus-022.mp3\" class=\"powerpress_link_d\" title=\"Download\" rel=\"